      "question_text": "20 mL of 0.1 M NH₄OH is mixed with 40 mL of 0.05 M HCl. The pH of the mixture is nearest to: (Given: K_b(NH₄OH) = 1×10⁻⁵, log 2 = 0.30, log 3 = 0.48)",
